%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: DEV_111_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7f02d918675a648eca21b48c24fe28e5, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1528243937280
    m_Localized: Welcome to this quest
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1528243937281
    m_Localized: The quest is complete.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1528243937282
    m_Localized: Why don't you do this homework?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1528243937283
    m_Localized: Hallo
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1528243937284
    m_Localized: I'm a Living Letter tourist
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711465877504
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Carrara marble quarries!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654720
    m_Localized: These white mountains are famous all over the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654721
    m_Localized: Great work today! The quarry is running again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654722
    m_Localized: You will never forget the secrets of the white mountain!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654723
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Come here, let me fix the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654724
    m_Localized: The machine is still broken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654725
    m_Localized: Please help me find the pieces.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654726
    m_Localized: Go ask the spirits of the quarry!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654727
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654728
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654729
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654730
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654731
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654732
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654733
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654734
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654735
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654736
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654737
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654738
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654739
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654740
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654741
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654742
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654743
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654744
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654745
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654746
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654747
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654748
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654749
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654750
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654751
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654752
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654753
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654754
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654755
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654756
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654757
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654758
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654759
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654760
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654761
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654762
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654763
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654764
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654765
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654766
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654767
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654768
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654769
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654770
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654771
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654772
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654773
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654774
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654775
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654776
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654777
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654778
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654779
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654780
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654781
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654782
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654783
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654784
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654785
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654786
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654787
    m_Localized: Find the five quarry tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654788
    m_Localized: Look carefully around you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654789
    m_Localized: You haven't found everything. Keep looking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654790
    m_Localized: The tools are hidden somewhere in this area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654791
    m_Localized: Let me show you where to look.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654792
    m_Localized: Look for the wedge, the mallet and the lizza.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654793
    m_Localized: Then the wire saw and the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654794
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654795
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654796
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654797
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654798
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654799
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654800
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654801
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654802
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654803
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654804
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654805
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654806
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654807
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654808
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654809
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654810
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654811
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654812
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654813
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654814
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654815
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654816
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654817
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654818
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654819
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654820
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654821
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654822
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654823
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654824
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654825
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654826
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654827
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654828
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654829
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654830
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654831
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654832
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654833
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654834
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654835
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654836
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654837
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654838
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654839
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654840
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654841
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654842
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654843
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654844
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654845
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654846
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654847
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654848
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654849
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654850
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654851
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2609711482654852
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743328923648
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Carrara marble quarries!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895168
    m_Localized: These white mountains are famous all over the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895169
    m_Localized: Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895170
    m_Localized: Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895171
    m_Localized: "Take a look at this machine \u2014 it's incredibly powerful!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895172
    m_Localized: Let me start it up...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895173
    m_Localized: Wait... it's not working!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895174
    m_Localized: Something's wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895175
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895176
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895177
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895178
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895179
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895180
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895181
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895182
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895183
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895184
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895185
    m_Localized: I chose this marble for the Baptistery of Pisa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895186
    m_Localized: But before making art... you need to extract the marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895187
    m_Localized: Let me explain how it has been done through the centuries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895188
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895189
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895190
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895191
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895192
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895193
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895194
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895195
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895196
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895197
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895198
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895199
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895200
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895201
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895202
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895203
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895204
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895205
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895206
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895207
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895208
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895209
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895210
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895211
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895212
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895213
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895214
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895215
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895216
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895217
    m_Localized: I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895218
    m_Localized: I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius
      II.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895219
    m_Localized: I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895220
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895221
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895222
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895223
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895224
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895225
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895226
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895227
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895228
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895229
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895230
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895231
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895232
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job that existed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895233
    m_Localized: Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895234
    m_Localized: Now I ask you to find the tools they used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895235
    m_Localized: Find the five quarry tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895236
    m_Localized: Look carefully around you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895237
    m_Localized: You haven't found everything. Keep looking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895238
    m_Localized: The tools are hidden somewhere in this area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895239
    m_Localized: Let me show you where to look.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895240
    m_Localized: Look for the wedge, the mallet and the lizza.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895241
    m_Localized: Then the wire saw and the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895242
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895243
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895244
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895245
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895246
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895247
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895248
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895249
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895250
    m_Localized: I changed the way marble was used forever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895251
    m_Localized: "Look at Apollo and Daphne \u2014 I carved it between 1622 and 1625."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895252
    m_Localized: I was only twenty-three years old when I began!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895253
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895254
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895255
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895256
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895257
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895258
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895259
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895260
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895261
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895262
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895263
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895264
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895265
    m_Localized: I wish I had had such a tool!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895266
    m_Localized: "But enough talking \u2014 put my sculpture back together!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895267
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895268
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895269
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895270
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895271
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895272
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895273
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895274
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895275
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895276
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895277
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895278
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895279
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895280
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895281
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895282
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895283
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895284
    m_Localized: 'Tell me: what is the technique we use today?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895285
    m_Localized: The diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895286
    m_Localized: Explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895287
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895288
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895289
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895290
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895291
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895292
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895293
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895294
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895295
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895296
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895297
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895298
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895299
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2697743349895300
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138112
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Carrara marble quarries!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138113
    m_Localized: These white mountains are famous all over the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138114
    m_Localized: Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138115
    m_Localized: Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138116
    m_Localized: "Take a look at this machine \u2014 it's incredibly powerful!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138117
    m_Localized: Let me start it up...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138118
    m_Localized: Wait... it's not working!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138119
    m_Localized: Something's wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138120
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138121
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138122
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138123
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138124
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138125
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138126
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138127
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138128
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138129
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138130
    m_Localized: I chose this marble for the Baptistery of Pisa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138131
    m_Localized: But before making art... you need to extract the marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138132
    m_Localized: Let me explain how it has been done through the centuries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138133
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138134
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138135
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138136
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138137
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138138
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138139
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138140
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138141
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138142
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138143
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138144
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138145
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138146
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138147
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138148
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138149
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138150
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138151
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138152
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138153
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138154
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138155
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138156
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138157
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138158
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138159
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138160
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138161
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138162
    m_Localized: I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138163
    m_Localized: I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius
      II.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138164
    m_Localized: I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138165
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138166
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138167
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138168
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138169
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138170
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138171
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138172
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138173
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138174
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138175
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138176
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138177
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job that existed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138178
    m_Localized: Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138179
    m_Localized: Now I ask you to find the tools they used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138180
    m_Localized: Find the five quarry tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138181
    m_Localized: Look carefully around you!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138182
    m_Localized: You haven't found everything. Keep looking.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138183
    m_Localized: The tools are hidden somewhere in this area.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138184
    m_Localized: Let me show you where to look.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138185
    m_Localized: Look for the wedge, the mallet and the lizza.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138186
    m_Localized: Then the wire saw and the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138187
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138188
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138189
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138190
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138191
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138192
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138193
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138194
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138195
    m_Localized: I changed the way marble was used forever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138196
    m_Localized: "Look at Apollo and Daphne \u2014 I carved it between 1622 and 1625."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138197
    m_Localized: I was only twenty-three years old when I began!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138198
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138199
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138200
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138201
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138202
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138203
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138204
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138205
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138206
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138207
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138208
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138209
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138210
    m_Localized: I wish I had had such a tool!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138211
    m_Localized: "But enough talking \u2014 put my sculpture back together!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138212
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138213
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138214
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138215
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138216
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138217
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138218
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138219
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138220
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138221
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138222
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138223
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138224
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138225
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138226
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138227
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138228
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138229
    m_Localized: 'Tell me: what is the technique we use today?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138230
    m_Localized: The diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138231
    m_Localized: Explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138232
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138233
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138234
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138235
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138236
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138237
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138238
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138239
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138240
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138241
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138242
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138243
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138244
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2896729346138245
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727653355520
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Carrara marble quarries!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298560
    m_Localized: These white mountains are famous all over the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298561
    m_Localized: Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298562
    m_Localized: Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298563
    m_Localized: "Take a look at this machine \u2014 it's incredibly powerful!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298564
    m_Localized: Let me start it up...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298565
    m_Localized: Wait... it's not working!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298566
    m_Localized: Something's wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298567
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298568
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298569
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298570
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298571
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298572
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298573
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298574
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298575
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298576
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298577
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298578
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298579
    m_Localized: I chose this marble for the Baptistery of Pisa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298580
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298581
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298582
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298583
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298584
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298585
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298586
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298587
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298588
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298589
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298590
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298591
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298592
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298593
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298594
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298595
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298596
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298597
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298598
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298599
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298600
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298601
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298602
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298603
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298604
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298605
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298606
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298607
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298608
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298609
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298610
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298611
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298612
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298613
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298614
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298615
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298616
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298617
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298618
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298619
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298620
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298621
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298622
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298623
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298624
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298625
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298626
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298627
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298628
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298629
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298630
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298631
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298632
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298633
    m_Localized: Then the wire saw and the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298634
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298635
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298636
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298637
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298638
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298639
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298640
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298641
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298642
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298643
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298644
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298645
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298646
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298647
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298648
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298649
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298650
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298651
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298652
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298653
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298654
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298655
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298656
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298657
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298658
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298659
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298660
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298661
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298662
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298663
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298664
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298665
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298666
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298667
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298668
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298669
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298670
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298671
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298672
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298673
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298674
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298675
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298676
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298677
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298678
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298679
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298680
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298681
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298682
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298683
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298684
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298685
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298686
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298687
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298688
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298689
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298690
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298691
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4437727695298692
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962304
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962305
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962306
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962307
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962308
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962309
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962310
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962311
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962312
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962313
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962314
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962315
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962316
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962317
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962318
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962319
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962320
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962321
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4438274468962322
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246350561280
    m_Localized: But before making art... you need to extract the marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755584
    m_Localized: Let me explain how it has been done through the centuries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755585
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755586
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755587
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755588
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755589
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755590
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755591
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755592
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755593
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755594
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755595
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755596
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755597
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755598
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755599
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755600
    m_Localized: I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755601
    m_Localized: I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius
      II.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755602
    m_Localized: I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755603
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755604
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755605
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755606
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755607
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755608
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job that existed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755609
    m_Localized: Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755610
    m_Localized: Now I ask you to draw what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755611
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755612
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755613
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755614
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755615
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755616
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755617
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755618
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755619
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755620
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755621
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755622
    m_Localized: I changed the way marble was used forever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755623
    m_Localized: "Look at Apollo and Daphne \u2014 I carved it between 1622 and 1625."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755624
    m_Localized: I was only twenty-three years old when I began!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755625
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755626
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755627
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755628
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755629
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755630
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755631
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755632
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755633
    m_Localized: I wish I had had such a tool!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755634
    m_Localized: "But enough talking \u2014 put my sculpture back together!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755635
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755636
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755637
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755638
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755639
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755640
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755641
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755642
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755643
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755644
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755645
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755646
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755647
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755648
    m_Localized: 'Tell me: what is the technique we use today?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755649
    m_Localized: The diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755650
    m_Localized: Explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755651
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755652
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755653
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755654
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755655
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755656
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755657
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755658
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755659
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755660
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755661
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755662
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755663
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755664
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755665
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755666
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4450246354755667
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119131
    m_Localized: Let me explain how it has been done through the centuries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119130
    m_Localized: But before making art... you need to extract the marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119129
    m_Localized: I chose this marble for the Baptistery of Pisa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119128
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119127
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119126
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119125
    m_Localized: You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119124
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885896
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885897
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885898
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885899
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885900
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885901
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885902
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885903
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885904
    m_Localized: Well done! You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885905
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885906
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885907
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119123
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119122
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119121
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885911
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885912
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885913
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885914
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885915
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885916
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885917
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885918
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885919
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885920
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885921
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885922
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885923
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885924
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885925
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885926
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885927
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885928
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885929
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885930
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885931
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885932
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885933
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885934
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885935
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885936
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885937
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885938
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885939
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885940
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885941
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119120
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119119
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119118
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885945
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885946
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885947
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885948
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885949
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885950
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885951
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885952
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885953
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885954
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885955
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885956
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119117
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119116
    m_Localized: Something's wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119115
    m_Localized: Wait... it's not working!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885960
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885961
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885962
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885963
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885964
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885965
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885966
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885967
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885968
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885969
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885970
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885971
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885972
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885973
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885974
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119114
    m_Localized: Let me start it up...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119113
    m_Localized: "Take a look at this machine \u2014 it's incredibly powerful!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119112
    m_Localized: Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119111
    m_Localized: Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885979
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885980
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885981
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885982
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885983
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119110
    m_Localized: Go ask the spirits of the quarry!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885985
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885986
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885987
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885988
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885989
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119109
    m_Localized: Please help me find the pieces.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119108
    m_Localized: The machine is still broken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119107
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Come here, let me fix the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885993
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885994
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885995
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885996
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885997
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885998
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198885999
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198886000
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198886001
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198886002
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198886003
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979198886004
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080192
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080193
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080194
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080195
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119106
    m_Localized: You will never forget the secrets of the white mountain!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119105
    m_Localized: Great work today! The quarry is running again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119104
    m_Localized: These white mountains are famous all over the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608538730496
    m_Localized: Welcome to the Carrara marble quarries!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080200
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080201
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080202
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080203
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080204
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080205
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080206
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080207
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080208
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080209
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080210
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080211
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080212
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080213
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080214
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080215
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4874979203080216
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703842979840
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951360
    m_Localized: You already have my piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951361
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951362
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951363
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951364
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951365
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951366
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951367
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951368
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951369
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951370
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951371
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951372
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951373
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951374
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951375
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951376
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951377
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951378
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951379
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951380
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951381
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951382
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951383
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951384
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951385
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951386
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951387
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951388
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951389
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951390
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951391
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951392
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951393
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951394
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951395
    m_Localized: Well done! You found everything.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951396
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951397
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951398
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951399
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951400
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951401
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951402
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951403
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951404
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951405
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951406
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951407
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951408
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951409
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951410
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951411
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951412
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951413
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951414
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951415
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951416
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951417
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951418
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951419
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951420
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951421
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951422
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951423
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951424
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951425
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951426
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951427
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951428
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951429
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951430
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951431
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951432
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951433
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951434
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951435
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951436
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951437
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951438
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951439
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951440
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951441
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951442
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5124703863951443
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584576
    m_Localized: The machine is still broken.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584577
    m_Localized: please help me fine the pieces
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584578
    m_Localized: go ask the spirits of the quarry!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584579
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584580
    m_Localized: I am Nicola Pisano, a medieval sculptor.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584581
    m_Localized: It was the year 1260 when I first came here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584582
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219842584583
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778880
    m_Localized: 'First technique: the wooden wedge.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778881
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778882
    m_Localized: 'Second technique: explosives.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778883
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778884
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778885
    m_Localized: 'Third technique: the diamond wire.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778886
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778887
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778888
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778889
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778890
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... diamond wire... explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778891
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778892
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778893
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778894
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778895
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778896
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778897
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778898
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778899
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778900
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778901
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778902
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778903
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778904
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778905
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778906
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778907
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778908
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778909
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778910
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778911
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778912
    m_Localized: You know the quarrymen's tools.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778913
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778914
    m_Localized: Magnificent! You understand the lizzatura.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778915
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778916
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778917
    m_Localized: I changed the way marble was used forever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778918
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219846778919
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973184
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973185
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973186
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973187
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973188
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973189
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973190
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973191
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973192
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973193
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973194
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973195
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973196
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973197
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973198
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973199
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973200
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973201
    m_Localized: 'Tell me: what is the technique we use today?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973202
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973203
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973204
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973205
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973206
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973207
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973208
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973209
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973210
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973211
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973212
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973213
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973214
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973215
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973216
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973217
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5139219850973218
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454737469440
    m_Localized: Hi! I'm Francesco, a quarry worker.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412480
    m_Localized: Today I'll show you how marble is extracted.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412481
    m_Localized: "Take a look at this machine \u2014 it's incredibly powerful!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412482
    m_Localized: Let me start it up...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412483
    m_Localized: Wait... it's not working!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412484
    m_Localized: Something's wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412485
    m_Localized: Antura! Was it you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412486
    m_Localized: Look what you've done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412487
    m_Localized: Three parts of the machine have fallen into the quarry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412488
    m_Localized: You need to find them!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412489
    m_Localized: Go and look for them.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412490
    m_Localized: Maybe the spirits of the quarry will help you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412491
    m_Localized: I chose this marble for the Baptistery of Pisa.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412492
    m_Localized: But before making art... you need to extract the marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412493
    m_Localized: Let me explain how it has been done through the centuries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412494
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412495
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412496
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412497
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412498
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412499
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412500
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412501
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412502
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412503
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412504
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412505
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412506
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... explosives... diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412507
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412508
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412509
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412510
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412511
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412512
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412513
    m_Localized: I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412514
    m_Localized: I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius
      II.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412515
    m_Localized: I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412516
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412517
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412518
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412519
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job that existed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412520
    m_Localized: Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412521
    m_Localized: Now I ask you to draw what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412522
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412523
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412524
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412525
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412526
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412527
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412528
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412529
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412530
    m_Localized: "Look at Apollo and Daphne \u2014 I carved it between 1622 and 1625."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412531
    m_Localized: I was only twenty-three years old when I began!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412532
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412533
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412534
    m_Localized: I wish I had had such a tool!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412535
    m_Localized: "But enough talking \u2014 put my sculpture back together!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412536
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412537
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412538
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412539
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412540
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412541
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412542
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412543
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412544
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454779412545
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606784
    m_Localized: The diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606785
    m_Localized: Explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606786
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606787
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606788
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606789
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606790
    m_Localized: Are you ready for the final test?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606791
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606792
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606793
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606794
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606795
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606796
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5211454783606797
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119132
    m_Localized: First technique\:he wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119133
    m_Localized: The Romans pushed fig-wood wedges into cracks in the rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119134
    m_Localized: "Then they soaked the wood \u2014 as it swelled, it split the stone!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119135
    m_Localized: Clever, wasn't it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119136
    m_Localized: Second technique\:explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119137
    m_Localized: From 1600 onwards, workers used gunpowder in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119138
    m_Localized: They blasted the mountainside to break off the blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119139
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed a lot of marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119140
    m_Localized: And the damage to the environment was enormous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119141
    m_Localized: Third technique\:the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119142
    m_Localized: Since 1970, a steel wire coated in industrial diamonds has been
      used.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119143
    m_Localized: It cuts the rock with perfect precision and no waste.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119144
    m_Localized: In one day, you can cut what once took three whole months!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119145
    m_Localized: 'Now tell me: can you match each technique to the right era?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119146
    m_Localized: Match each technique to its correct era.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119147
    m_Localized: You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119148
    m_Localized: Almost! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119149
    m_Localized: Wooden wedge... explosives... diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119150
    m_Localized: All right, let me help you a little.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119151
    m_Localized: The Romans used the wooden wedge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119152
    m_Localized: In the 1600s they used explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119153
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119154
    m_Localized: Excellent! You've understood it well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119155
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119156
    m_Localized: Now go find the other spirits.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119157
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119158
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119159
    m_Localized: You already have my piece. Good!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119160
    m_Localized: Go find the other spirit.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119161
    m_Localized: I am Michelangelo Buonarroti.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119162
    m_Localized: Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119163
    m_Localized: I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119164
    m_Localized: I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius
      II.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119165
    m_Localized: I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119166
    m_Localized: Marble is not just a rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119167
    m_Localized: It is the most living material in existence.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119168
    m_Localized: The sculpture is already inside the block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119169
    m_Localized: My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119170
    m_Localized: With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119171
    m_Localized: Works that will last for thousands of years.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119172
    m_Localized: But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119173
    m_Localized: These blocks weigh as much as ten cars.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119174
    m_Localized: There were no trucks, no trains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119175
    m_Localized: 'They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119176
    m_Localized: The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119177
    m_Localized: They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119178
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job that existed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119179
    m_Localized: Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119180
    m_Localized: Now I ask you to draw what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119181
    m_Localized: Draw the lizza on the canvas.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119182
    m_Localized: Show me you understood!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119183
    m_Localized: Not quite right. Try again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119184
    m_Localized: 'Remember: a sled on a steep slope, with ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119185
    m_Localized: Let me show you. A wooden sled on steep rock.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119186
    m_Localized: Thick ropes holding it back.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119187
    m_Localized: Magnificent! You understand the lizzatura.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119188
    m_Localized: Take this piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119189
    m_Localized: Now go find Bernini.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119190
    m_Localized: The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119191
    m_Localized: Go find Francesco first.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119192
    m_Localized: You already have my piece! Well done, young artist.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119193
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119194
    m_Localized: I am Gian Lorenzo Bernini!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119195
    m_Localized: Sculptor, architect, painter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119196
    m_Localized: I changed the way marble was used forever.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119197
    m_Localized: "Look at Apollo and Daphne \u2014 I carved it between 1622 and 1625."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119198
    m_Localized: I was only twenty-three years old when I began!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119199
    m_Localized: This sculpture captures the exact moment Daphne transforms into
      a laurel tree.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119200
    m_Localized: Her fingers become branches, her feet roots, her skin bark.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119201
    m_Localized: "All of this in marble \u2014 a rock as hard as iron!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119202
    m_Localized: No one before me had dared to attempt such a thing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119203
    m_Localized: People believed marble could never look soft.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119204
    m_Localized: I proved them wrong.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119205
    m_Localized: In my time, marble was cut with chisels and mallets.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119206
    m_Localized: Every millimetre was sweat and effort.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119207
    m_Localized: 'Today there is the diamond wire: a steel wire coated in industrial
      diamonds.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119208
    m_Localized: It runs at hundreds of metres per minute.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119209
    m_Localized: It slices through marble like butter, with no waste at all.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119210
    m_Localized: In a single day you can do the work that in my time took three months.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119211
    m_Localized: I wish I had had such a tool!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119212
    m_Localized: "But enough talking \u2014 put my sculpture back together!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119213
    m_Localized: Reassemble the pieces of Apollo and Daphne.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119214
    m_Localized: Four pieces. You can do it!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119215
    m_Localized: Not yet! Try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119216
    m_Localized: Look at the shape of each piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119217
    m_Localized: I'll give you a little help this time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119218
    m_Localized: Start with the largest piece.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119219
    m_Localized: Magnificent! The work is whole again!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119220
    m_Localized: Carrara marble is unique in all the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119221
    m_Localized: Take the last piece of the machine.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119222
    m_Localized: You have all three pieces!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119223
    m_Localized: Go back to Francesco.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119224
    m_Localized: You found all the pieces! Thank you so much!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119225
    m_Localized: I'm putting the machine back together...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119226
    m_Localized: There we go! Let's try it now.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119227
    m_Localized: It works! Can you hear the wire?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119228
    m_Localized: Today Carrara has 165 active quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119229
    m_Localized: The marble leaves by ship from the port to the whole world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119230
    m_Localized: 'Tell me: what is the technique we use today?'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119231
    m_Localized: The diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119232
    m_Localized: Explosives.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119233
    m_Localized: Exactly! It cuts like butter.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119234
    m_Localized: And it does far less damage to the environment.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119235
    m_Localized: You're really smart!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119236
    m_Localized: We used that in the old days.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119237
    m_Localized: It was fast, but it destroyed too much marble.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119238
    m_Localized: Today we use the diamond wire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119239
    m_Localized: You've learned so much today.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119240
    m_Localized: Let me ask you one last question!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119241
    m_Localized: Let's see what you remember!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119242
    m_Localized: Time to answer the questions about the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119243
    m_Localized: Try again! Use what you have learned.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119244
    m_Localized: You fixed the machine!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119245
    m_Localized: You met three great artists.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119246
    m_Localized: Now you know how Carrara marble is born.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119247
    m_Localized: Draw your own marble block.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119248
    m_Localized: What would you sculpt?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5244608547119249
    m_Localized: Tell someone at home where Carrara marble comes from.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508540125184
    m_Localized: Well done! Now for the second question.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039744
    m_Localized: Excellent! One last question to go!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039745
    m_Localized: Outstanding! You know your marble!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039746
    m_Localized: You have truly learned the secrets of the white mountain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039747
    m_Localized: "From the lizza to the diamond wire \u2014"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039748
    m_Localized: you now carry the whole history of Carrara in your mind.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10798508603039749
    m_Localized: I couldn't have wished for a better explorer today. Well done!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325143293952
    m_Localized: In the old days, how did the quarrymen bring marble blocks down
      the mountain?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848384
    m_Localized: On the lizza, a wooden sled.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848385
    m_Localized: By river on boats.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848386
    m_Localized: On the backs of oxen and horses.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848387
    m_Localized: "Exactly right! The lizza \u2014 a heavy wooden sled guided down
      steep slopes with thick hemp ropes."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848388
    m_Localized: Incredibly dangerous, but the only way to move such enormous blocks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848389
    m_Localized: 'Not quite! The quarrymen used the lizza: a heavy wooden sled slid
      down steep slopes with thick hemp ropes.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10807325176848390
    m_Localized: It was the most dangerous job in the quarries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
